Sign In Please 1984


Sign In Please is the 1984 debut album by the American rock band Autograph. The album featured their signature song, &quot;Turn Up the Radio,&quot; and their other minor hit, &quot;Send Her to Me,&quot; both of which had accompanying videos.

&quot;Turn Up the Radio&quot; was featured in the opening credits of the 2010 movie Hot Tub Time Machine, the video game Grand Theft Auto: Vice City as well as the Obsidian RPG, Alpha Protocol, while &quot;All I'm Gonna Take&quot; was featured in Grand Theft Auto: Vice City Stories.



